<TEXT>
Computer   Systems Using Walsh and Fourier Transforms 

<F P=102> 947G0012A Kiev IZVESTIYA VYSSHIKH UCHEBNYKH ZAVEDENIY: 
RADIOELEKTRONIKA in Russian No .9, Sep 93 pp 34-40--FOR OFFICIAL </F>

