<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Sorption of Copper Ions With VION KN-1 Chemosorption Fiber </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   947M0008A Mytishchi KHIMICHESKIYE VOLOKNA in Russian No. 5, 
Sep-Oct 93 pp 27-29 </F>

<F P=103> 947M0008A </F>
<F P=104>  Mytishchi KHIMICHESKIYE VOLOKNA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


